task.summary: Using new version of service bus library on Azure with net standard support. Added service bus sender queue.
Handing duplicate columns names between key and value on SqlSetMap
SqlExpressionTranslator is now always using SQL parameters instead of raw value strings on generated SQL
Passing DbTypeMapper to expression translator to create parameters with correct types
Added test for complex type on SqlQueryTranslator
Handling null parameters values with IS NULL instead of passing DbNull.Value argument that is not working
Kafka receiver now has lazy initialization. Adjusted unit tests.
Fixed SQL server support for concurrent add if not exists on Map implementation
